-- MOVES-EY names Andrew Gallacher as head of advisory for Swiss insurance
-- By Aurindom Mukherjee
-- Wed Dec 17, 2014 04:06AM EST
-- None



Dec 17 (Reuters) - Auditing firm Ernst & Young LLP [ERNY.UL] appointed Andrew Gallacher as a partner and head of advisory for the insurance industry in Switzerland.

Gallacher previously worked with Deloitte [DLTE.UL] as a partner for insurance industry, according to his LinkedIn profile, handling various clients in the Swiss insurance sector and other European countries. Gallacher also worked for various global risk and finance operations with both Zurich Insurance Group Ltd and Axa.